                <h1> Arctic Hare </h1>
                <p> The Arctic Hare also known as the Polar rabbit is a species of hare that tends to live in the tundra Biome. They are hunted by Arctic Wolves and they eat berries,buds, branches ,etc.! their life span is around 5 years.</p>
